---
import Eyebrow from './Eyebrow.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[220px_1fr] gap-10 items-start reveal">
    <div class="shrink-0">
      <img src="https://placehold.co/440x440/f8fafc/cbd5e1?text=Your+Photo" alt="Instructor" loading="lazy"
           class="w-40 h-40 md:w-full md:h-auto aspect-square object-cover rounded-2xl border border-gray-200" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <Eyebrow text="Who teaches this" />
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-950 mt-3">REPLACE — Your name here</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        REPLACE with your real background: how long you have traded, what you specialise in, any funded accounts or prop firms passed, and why you built this curriculum. Keep it honest and specific — this is where trust is won or lost.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>REPLACE — a real, verifiable credential</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>REPLACE — years of experience / focus</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>REPLACE — what makes your approach different</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
